^ Scileppi, John A.; Elizabeth lee Teed, Robin Diller Torres. Community Psychology: A Common Sense Approach to Mental Health . Prentice Hall. 2000. ISBN 0-13-083341-X.  引文使用過時參數coauthors (幫助)
